{"word":"G4374 - προσφέρω - prosphérō - pros-fer'-o - Bring","slug":"G4374","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προσφέρω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>prosphérō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>pros-fer'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bring"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03C3;&#x03C6;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03C9; - prosphero&#x0304;</b> - <i>pros-fer'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4314\">G4314</a> and <a href=\"#/G5342\">G5342</a> (including its alternate); to <i>bear towards</i>, that is, <i>lead to</i>, <i>tender</i> (especially to God), <i>treat:</i> - bring (to, unto), deal with, do, offer (unto, up), present unto, put to."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1308\">G1308</a>, <a href=\"#/G1313\">G1313</a>, <a href=\"#/G2018\">G2018</a>, <a href=\"#/G399\">G399</a>, <a href=\"#/G4376\">G4376</a>, <a href=\"#/G4851\">G4851</a>, <a href=\"#/G5342\">G5342</a>, <a href=\"#/G5409\">G5409</a>, <a href=\"#/G5411\">G5411</a>, <a href=\"#/G5412\">G5412</a>, <a href=\"#/G5413\">G5413</a>, <a href=\"#/G5414\">G5414</a>"}]}